---
title: Chicken and Chickpea Korma Crumble with Kale
description: We love good Chicken and Chickpea Korma Crumble and this deliciously simple, chef-curated recipe doesn't disappoint. Time to bust out the pots and pans!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/chicken-and-chickpea-korma-crumble-98650a5a-8888e209.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.uk/recipecards/card/chicken-and-chickpea-korma-crumble-5e3d990d78eb9e55a64e7c87-a71577aa.pdf
